ProtoDefines:
. "A sequence of points $\{\mathbf{X}_r\}$ in $\R^n$ {\it 
   converges to the limit } $\overline{\mathbf{X}}$ if $$ 
   \lim_{r\to\infty} |\mathbf{X}_r-\overline{\mathbf{X}}|=0. $$
   In this case we write $$ 
   \lim_{r\to\infty}\mathbf{X}_r=\overline{\mathbf{X}}. $$"
